      "id": "la28",
      "name": "LA28 Account Generator",
      "description": "LA28 ticket account generator: passes the waiting room, keeps the queue session alive, switches to the sign-up form, fills the profile details (name, email, password, country, zip), confirms the email verification code, and saves the account. It fails fast on Restricted-access pages (blocked IP/region) and unsupported queue picture-code challenges, and best-effort accepts the legal-terms popup. Runs with or without a Profile Group - on None it uses a generated identity and address, so all it needs is an email source (Key Vault mailboxes, an AYCD list, or a catchall domain). Fails fast with \"email already used\" if the address is already registered from a prior Olympic & Paralympic Games.",
